Package CircoloVelico.unipr.it

Class MemberService

java.lang.Object
CircoloVelico.unipr.it.MemberService
public class MemberService extends Object
The MemberService class is used to send to the server request objects. Its methods receive all data which must be send to the server from different form that user complete.

    • signUp

      public ResponseSignMember signUp(String username, String password, int reqvalue)
      This function is used from the MemberSignInController to SignUp a user. All the information that user enter into the form will be sent to the server into a request object. Request object that is used is RequestSignMember.
      Parameters:
      username - is the username entered by the user.
      password - is the passeword entered by the user.
      reqvalue - this param is used to distinguish which request client is making to the server.
      Returns:
      It returns a response object that contain the answer send by the server.
